---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Recent Projects - Advanced Biomass Consulting">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Recent Projects</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Selected biomass handling and processing projects completed by Advanced Biomass Consulting
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Biomass Processing Facility Design</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Complete system design for a 50 MW biomass power plant including fuel receiving, 
            processing, and storage systems. Handled multiple feedstock types including forest 
            residues, mill residues, and agricultural biomass.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">System Design</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Power Generation</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Multi-Feedstock</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2023</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Wood Pellet Handling System Upgrade</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Upgraded pellet handling systems for increased throughput and reduced degradation. 
            Implemented custom helical chutes and gentle handling equipment to maintain pellet 
            quality throughout the process.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Wood Pellets</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Gentle Handling</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">System Upgrade</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2022</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Biomass Sampling System Design</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Custom-designed production biomass sampling systems for quality control. 
            Systems were third-party evaluated and shown to be within the statistical 
            accuracy of laboratory sampling methods.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Sampling Systems</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Quality Control</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Custom Design</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2021</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Northern Climate Conveyor Systems</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Specialized conveyor design for extreme northern climates with temperatures 
            reaching -40Â°C. Implemented cold-weather materials, heated components, and 
            specialized enclosures for year-round operation.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Cold Climate</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Conveyor Systems</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Extreme Conditions</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2020</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Pulp Mill Chip Storage Optimization</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Optimization of chip storage and reclaim systems for improved inventory management 
            and reduced material degradation. Included pile compaction analysis and automated 
            pile management systems.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Pulp Mill</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Storage Systems</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Optimization</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2019</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Rock Removal System Implementation</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Design and implementation of rock and debris removal systems for forest residue 
            processing. Integrated multiple separation technologies to achieve high removal 
            efficiency with minimal biomass loss.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Rock Removal</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Forest Residues</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Separation Technology</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Completed: 2018</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Interested in Working Together?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Advanced Biomass Consulting brings decades of experience to every project. 
            Contact us to discuss your biomass handling challenges and project requirements.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>